        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         As a general rule I would say you need to be at least level 50 to hunt with some relatively safety in this zone. Assuming you want to get your epic piece, you would need either 2 level 55+ groups, or one level 59+ group to hold the Grand Herbalist Mak'ha camp. Things in there repop fast, not easy to split even at 60 and things tend to get hairy fast. Good CC is needed here, you rely on your chanter(s) a lot. Mobsin that area tend to be in the 50-58 level range. Snare everything (they all have this fucking annoying "indoor SoW" on them), stun casters so they dont gate. It's fun, an intense camp.</P><P><center><img src="http://home.t-online.de/home/iranicus/images/iranicus_lotj.jpg"><br><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=12328" target="_new">My Gear</a><BR></center><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
